  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/03f73c10687c2802a1128561d688803e.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The year is 2112, and the world is no longer the same. In the crumbling remains of a country once known as England, Detective Matthew Wallace—a man with a mysterious past—works as a private investigator. After returning from the Third World War, Matthew takes on an off-the-record case with only one ally: Abigail, a resourceful young secretary. Together, they uncover the dark secrets of the city’s elite while confronting shadows from Matthew’s past in a series of interconnected cases.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>***** SHORT GAME NOTICE </strong>*****</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DeTechtive 2112 offers a <strong>short, story-driven experience</strong> that can typically be completed in around <strong>3 hours</strong>, featuring <strong>high replayability</strong> through its case-based structure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the main campaign, the game also includes an <strong>extra Cyber Zombie Mode</strong> for players seeking more action after the story ends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/b5c2d9ac638158d1fa87e5a97b733645.poster.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/b5c2d9ac638158d1fa87e5a97b733645.webm?t=1760915254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/b5c2d9ac638158d1fa87e5a97b733645.mp4?t=1760915254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/a46d55325dd9542c33ecb58c023d965c.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into 5 unique cases, each with its own gripping mini-story, distinct map, and atmospheric locations. Every case offers new challenges and mysteries. The choice of how to approach and solve them—stealth, strategy, or all-out combat—is entirely yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/f004ea3cd47b514897cee7da34632b21.poster.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/f004ea3cd47b514897cee7da34632b21.webm?t=1760915254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/f004ea3cd47b514897cee7da34632b21.mp4?t=1760915254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/5f0fc6eb18972139a1d432d740f4a726.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience <i>DeTechtive 2112</i>, a story-driven action-adventure where up to 4 players can team up to solve a grand mystery across unique maps and gripping cases. Engage in thrilling combat against enemies or use stealth to take down foes silently and strategically. Whether you choose to fight, sneak, or outwit your enemies, every decision will bring you closer to unraveling the truth—and learning whether some things are better left undiscovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/54d904b6157e5edc63f571e70282050d.poster.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/54d904b6157e5edc63f571e70282050d.webm?t=1760915254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/54d904b6157e5edc63f571e70282050d.mp4?t=1760915254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/e8c2c23b4eb489a4b6ccc0d44975b5e5.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a rain-soaked, neon-lit city brought to life with Unreal Engine 5. With a striking noir cyberpunk aesthetic, atmospheric detail, and a unique narrative experience, <i>DeTechtive 2112</i> invites you to explore shadowed alleys, flickering neon signs, and towering skyscrapers—where every corner holds a story waiting to be uncovered. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/2484042ec0a5e7ba82d75064fe5634e0.poster.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/2484042ec0a5e7ba82d75064fe5634e0.webm?t=1760915254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/2484042ec0a5e7ba82d75064fe5634e0.mp4?t=1760915254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/03f73c10687c2802a1128561d688803e.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The year is 2112, and the world is no longer the same. In the crumbling remains of a country once known as England, Detective Matthew Wallace—a man with a mysterious past—works as a private investigator. After returning from the Third World War, Matthew takes on an off-the-record case with only one ally: Abigail, a resourceful young secretary. Together, they uncover the dark secrets of the city’s elite while confronting shadows from Matthew’s past in a series of interconnected cases.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>***** SHORT GAME NOTICE </strong>*****</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DeTechtive 2112 offers a <strong>short, story-driven experience</strong> that can typically be completed in around <strong>3 hours</strong>, featuring <strong>high replayability</strong> through its case-based structure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the main campaign, the game also includes an <strong>extra Cyber Zombie Mode</strong> for players seeking more action after the story ends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/b5c2d9ac638158d1fa87e5a97b733645.poster.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/b5c2d9ac638158d1fa87e5a97b733645.webm?t=1760915254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/b5c2d9ac638158d1fa87e5a97b733645.mp4?t=1760915254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/a46d55325dd9542c33ecb58c023d965c.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into 5 unique cases, each with its own gripping mini-story, distinct map, and atmospheric locations. Every case offers new challenges and mysteries. The choice of how to approach and solve them—stealth, strategy, or all-out combat—is entirely yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/f004ea3cd47b514897cee7da34632b21.poster.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/f004ea3cd47b514897cee7da34632b21.webm?t=1760915254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/f004ea3cd47b514897cee7da34632b21.mp4?t=1760915254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/5f0fc6eb18972139a1d432d740f4a726.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience <i>DeTechtive 2112</i>, a story-driven action-adventure where up to 4 players can team up to solve a grand mystery across unique maps and gripping cases. Engage in thrilling combat against enemies or use stealth to take down foes silently and strategically. Whether you choose to fight, sneak, or outwit your enemies, every decision will bring you closer to unraveling the truth—and learning whether some things are better left undiscovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/54d904b6157e5edc63f571e70282050d.poster.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/54d904b6157e5edc63f571e70282050d.webm?t=1760915254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/54d904b6157e5edc63f571e70282050d.mp4?t=1760915254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/e8c2c23b4eb489a4b6ccc0d44975b5e5.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a rain-soaked, neon-lit city brought to life with Unreal Engine 5. With a striking noir cyberpunk aesthetic, atmospheric detail, and a unique narrative experience, <i>DeTechtive 2112</i> invites you to explore shadowed alleys, flickering neon signs, and towering skyscrapers—where every corner holds a story waiting to be uncovered. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/2484042ec0a5e7ba82d75064fe5634e0.poster.avif?t=1760915254\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/2484042ec0a5e7ba82d75064fe5634e0.webm?t=1760915254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808800/extras/2484